        <div class="row">
          <h3>Why Choose Sidda musicals?</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Expert Faculty:</strong> Our team of qualified maestros,
            both from India and abroad, bring a wealth of knowledge and
            expertise. They create a conducive environment for learners,
            ensuring individual attention and personalized guidance.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Internationally Benchmarked Curriculum:</strong> Sidda
            musicals follows an internationally benchmarked curriculum. We
            explore various vocal styles of Western music, including pop, rock,
            jazz, and more.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Range, Tone, and Style:</strong> Expand your vocal
            capabilities with us. From hitting the right notes to perfecting
            your tone and style, our courses cover it all.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Performance Opportunities:</strong> We encourage stage
            performances and music workshops. Gain confidence and sharpen your
            vocal skills while expressing your artistic flair.
          </p>
