          <ul>
            <strong>Foundation Level (6-8 Months):</strong>
            <li>Develop a strong singing foundation.</li>
            <li>
              Learn breath management, effective posture, and vocal warm-ups.
            </li>
            <li>Understand basic terms used in Western music.</li>
            <li>Explore major scales, rhythm, and melodies.</li>
          </ul>
          <ul>
            <strong>Intermediate Levels:</strong>
            <li>
              Dive deeper into scales, improvisation, and voice modulation.
            </li>
            <li>
              Harmonize, explore different vocal registers, and work on tone
              placement.
            </li>
            <li>Perform on our digital stage and showcase your talent.</li>
          </ul>
          <ul>
            <strong>Advanced Levels:</strong>
            <li>
